---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contacto | Victoria Vallejos" sideBarActiveItemID="contacto">
  <div class="mt-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">Contacto</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-base-content/90">Redes y Canales Personales</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-base-content/70">
      Conectemos a nivel profesional, revisa mis proyectos técnicos o escríbeme directamente a mis canales informales.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/TU_LINKEDIN" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-base-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-2xl">💼</span>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm text-base-content">LinkedIn</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-base-content/60">Conectemos profesionalmente</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/TU_INSTAGRAM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-base-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-2xl">📸</span>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm text-base-content">Instagram</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-base-content/60">Un vistazo más cercano</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://github.com/Victopvl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-base-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-2xl">💻</span>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm text-base-content">GitHub</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-base-content/60">Mi código y repositorios</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="https://wa.me/56949745464" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-base-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-2xl">🟢</span>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm text-base-content">WhatsApp</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-base-content/60">Escríbeme un mensaje directo</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="mailto:victoriapaz.sa@gmail.com" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-base-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-2xl">✉️</span>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm text-base-content">Correo Electrónico</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-base-content/60">victoriapaz.sa@gmail.com</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/projects" class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-base-300 hover:bg-base-300 hover:border-base-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-2xl">🚀</span>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-sm text-base-content">Ver Proyectos</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-base-content/60">Explora mi portafolio técnico</div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider my-10"></div>

  <div class="mt-6 bg-base-200 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-base-300 flex flex-col items-center shadow-sm">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-1 text-primary">Datavolve</h2>
    <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-center mb-4 text-base-content/70">Consultoría TI & Transformación Digital</h3>
    
    <p class="text-sm text-center mb-6 max-w-md text-base-content/80 balance">
      Si buscas automatizar procesos, implementar soluciones de Inteligencia Artificial o requieres asesoría estratégica para tu empresa, coordinemos una reunión corporativa.
    </p>
    
    <a 
      href="https://taplink.cc/datavolve"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="btn btn-primary px-8 font-semibold shadow-md text-sm tracking-wide normal-case"
    >
      📅 Agendar una Consultoría
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>